| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1568 — Recovery Inhibition (dragonforce)"
| comment "Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 711283e5-5ab9-550c-a184-6e5e9653b1ed"
